            Computer Science student studying at Falmouth University. I have
            experince in programming and web design.
          </p>
          <div class="btn-container"> <!-- Find more about me button -->
            <button onclick="location.href='../about.html'" class="btn-default btn-about">Find out more ></button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    <!------------------ PROJECTS ---------------------->

      <div class="section color3">
        <div class="content section-padding information white-text">
          <h1>Projects</h1>
